7.0.0.name: wordpress/easy-csv-importer-2
7.0.0.description: CSV importer plugin for Wordpress. This is the first truly easy auto-blogger on Wordpress. Upload any CSV file to Wordpress, no need to change headers, create a template with a WYSIWYG editor within minutes then click to create posts. Our ECI plugin gets around the problems other importers have by requiring minimum options to be used on the interface and it breaks larger operations down into more steps with more monitoring. Our team is always standing by to help make it even easier.
